-Meryem...

280
00:21:50,858 --> 00:21:54,749
M. Alam will ask me about you.

281
00:21:55,267 --> 00:21:58,355
What should I tell him?

282
00:21:58,355 --> 00:22:02,205
Whatever you feel like telling him.

283
