308
00:24:29,908 --> 00:24:32,610
Meryem told me.

309
00:24:37,125 --> 00:24:38,408
Meryem?

310
00:24:38,408 --> 00:24:39,200
Yes.

311
00:24:39,200 --> 00:24:43,393
The same Meryem you've been looking for.

312
00:24:43,393 --> 00:24:46,125
How'd she find out?

313
00:24:46,125 --> 00:24:49,081
She lives in Murree.

314
00:24:50,544 --> 00:24:52,952
Meryem's in -- Murree?

315
00:24:52,952 --> 00:24:55,938
I was just as surprised as you are.

316
00:24:55,938 --> 00:25:00,333
All this while, the one you'd been looking for

317
00:25:00,333 --> 00:25:03,202
Had been living under the roof you'd given,

318
00:25:03,202 --> 00:25:06,057
And you hadn't a clue...

319
00:25:07,276 --> 00:25:09,800
There's something else you should know.

320
00:25:09,800 --> 00:25:13,799
Meryem's agreed to meet you.

321
00:25:15,360 --> 00:25:16,961
