-Yes. I --

331
00:25:41,008 --> 00:25:44,657
No, Malik, I can't wait anymore.

332
00:25:44,657 --> 00:25:49,000
You don't know how I've longed to see this day.

333
00:25:49,000 --> 00:25:53,537
Prayed day and night for just one thing...

334
00:25:53,537 --> 00:25:55,987
That I get to meet her once.

335
00:25:55,987 --> 00:26:00,740
I want to ask for her forgiveness.

336
00:26:01,273 --> 00:26:06,719
